Description_lang: You find additional fragments when looting archaeological finds and you can survey faster than normal archaeologists.

description_blz.en_US: You find additional fragments when looting archaeological finds and you can survey faster than normal archaeologists.

description_blz.ko_KR: 고고학적 발견 시 추가 조각을 획득하고 일반 탐험가보다 조사 속도가 빠릅니다.
